been selected and encouraged precisely for your borderline-crazy optimism a=
nd self-confidence. You can=E2=80=99t do impossible things unless you first=
 believe that you can, etc.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">If you are cert=
ain that you will succeed brilliantly in all your endeavors, then often the=
