ope=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important=
; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-sty=
le: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> can also be securities fraud on your s=
hareholders</a>. It is a stretch, though, and in any case more the sort of =
thing a plaintiffs=E2=80=99 lawyer would argue against a public company tha=
n what a federal prosecutor would argue against a private company.</p><p st=
yle=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But, nah, there is a simpler explanation. From the =
<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/23691468.287938/aH=
R0cHM6Ly9hc3NldHMuYndieC5pby9kb2N1bWVudHMvdXNlcnMvaXFqV0hCRmRmeElVL3JBOVE2V=
