ant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-=
style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">charges against them</a>:</p><blockq=
uote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Defendant DEVON LUNA =E2=80=A6=C2=A0did k=
nowingly make, utter, and possess, and cause to be made, uttered and posses=
sed, forged and counterfeited securities of the State of Texas, with the in=
tent to deceive other persons, organizations, and governments; specifically=
, Defendant DEVON LUNA altered and caused to be altered the existing Texas =
titles of the vehicles listed below, by writing the false mileages listed b=
elow, to deceive automobile dealerships and individuals regarding the vehic=
les=E2=80=99 true mileages =E2=80=A6=C2=A0In violation of Title 18, United =
States Code, Section 513(a).</p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">T=
hat=E2=80=99s not the <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/cl=
ick/23691468.287938/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubGF3LmNvcm5lbGwuZWR1L3VzY29kZS90ZXh0LzE=
1Lzc4ag/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB8c030524" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=
=3D"itemscope" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; b=
order-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style:=
 solid; background-color: #ccc;">regular securities fraud law</a>, which fo=
rbids =E2=80=9Cany manipulative or deceptive device=E2=80=9D in connection =
with the purchase or sale of any security. That=E2=80=99s a <a href=3D"http=
s://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/23691468.287938/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cub=
GF3LmNvcm5lbGwuZWR1L3VzY29kZS90ZXh0LzE4LzUxMw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBad57=
