m-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">spec=
ial one</a>, which prohibits deceiving people with a forged or counterfeite=
d =E2=80=9Csecurity=C2=A0of a State or a political subdivision thereof or o=
f an organization.=E2=80=9D Apparently an automobile title counts as a secu=
rity of a state. So if you mess with a car title document, that=E2=80=99s s=
ecurities fraud. Good to know.</p><h2 style=3D"font-weight: bold; font-fami=
